com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.entity

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.mod.JsRegisteredClass
      • com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.mod.MinecraftClassWrapper
        • com.pcr3w.jscraft.minecraft.entity.Entity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IWrapper
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EntityLivingBase, ItemEntity, LightningBoltEntity

    public class Entity
extends MinecraftClassWrapper
    This class wraps around a Minecraft entity and allows all of the methods and fields to be accessed
    Author:
    pcr3w
